      info home http://eongames.com/games/sdlroids
      desc 'sdlroids is an asteroids clone.

sdlroids is essentially an Asteroids clone, 
but with a few extra features and some nice game physics.
It is based on xhyperoids, an UNIX port 
of an old Windows game called Hyperoids.'
